lead_paragraph: World number three Rory McIlroy gave himself a timely boost for this month's U.S. Open by ending a week of superb putting and accurate driving with a four-under 68 in the final round of the Memorial tournament on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Strong Memorial Finish Gives McIlroy a U.S. Open Fillip
